	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=51673"><span id=" ">rayash, Eater of Souls</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">93 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Default [2.27]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>As I said that was a template, if someone isn't dedicated enough to do as many as it takes to get the item then there are lower ones that would be only a few runs through, use the search feature and look for Type 3.<br/>My post was to inspire thinking of your own for filling in the slots (those just happen to be what I would choose for this robe if I needed it)<br/><br/>So instead of sayin hey, I don't wanna do what it would take to get that.....here are some more ideas for augs for this robe for lower levels.....(was assuming 102 pts for a 65 hard adventure on the augs above)<br/><br/><br/><br/>Jagged Ore of Foresight (AUG)&nbsp;&nbsp;0.0 Wt <br/>Slot types: 3  340 AP East Commonlands  Extended Range III<br/> 20  (will carry ya to 60+)<br/><br/>Grainy Sandstone of Clarity (AUG)  0.0 Wt <br/>Slot types: 3  340 AP Northern Desert of Ro  No Effects 20  (FT1)<br/><br/>Broken Limestone of Focus (AUG)  0.0 Wt <br/>Slot types: 3  60 AP Southern Desert of Ro  Spell Haste II  (nuff to get gate hasted)<br/><br/><br/>These are just &quot;suggestions&quot;, don't slam my suggestions :P make some more that the lower levels might be able to shoot for.<br/><br/></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br /><a href=HTTP://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?44381 target=akztarg>Sindu </a><br/>Dark Elf Hunter</td></tr>
